Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.82,0:00:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shu! Open this for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are you going out somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been over this! My club's going on a vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, I sort of feel like you told me that... did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.05,0:00:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to be home for a while, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.26,0:00:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you're leaving me here all alone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.05,0:00:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my fault, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.50,0:00:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll be {\i1}lonely{\i0}! I'm coming with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.03,0:00:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, you're heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.92,0:00:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori! Shu says he's abandoning me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, okay? Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.30,0:00:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to Oshima, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.49,0:00:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.68,0:00:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pay your father a visit, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here, we're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice day! I'm so glad it's not raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I hear we're heading to your family's vacation house?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah. I lived here when I was a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.76,0:02:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you're a lifesaver!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tamadate Souta?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the one in my class?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Bring him to Oshima. We're going to infiltrate a GHQ facility there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need his Void's power to break through their security.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all people...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you have to do is invite him on a trip. You can't tell me that's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good. Always cherish your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.01,0:03:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stupid Gai. He doesn't understand my feelings{darkness} at all.{NOBODY CARES}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! This place is so fancy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.37,0:03:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do your folks do for a living, Ouma?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai said the Kuhouin Group arranged it for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you two go getting affectionate again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.48,0:03:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save it for when you're at home, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where did {\i1}that{\i0} come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}do{\i0} live together, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:04:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught 'em in the act! They were going home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ask the couple. How did your romance begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, stop it! There's nothing between Inori and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's got a violent older brother, and I happened to know her, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.55,0:04:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah. We don't need to hear excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave the lovebirds alone and go hit the beach! Beach time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, shouldn't we unpack and—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're at a resort, guys! We gotta have all the fun we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tamadate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're at the beach! Woo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.87,0:04:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.51,0:04:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, he's so pushy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just being himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.59,0:04:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have a hard time dealing with Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's pushy, he has no tact, and he's oblivious to everyone around him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If it weren't for this mission, I'd never go on a trip with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A trip...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I let my guard down, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.49,0:05:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Hare!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go swim with them!{dem tits be bitchin'}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh.. um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.65,0:05:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.40,0:05:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.98,0:05:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hare!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Tamadate Souta made it here without issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's having way too much fun for someone on a mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we really be lettin' them goof off?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.89,0:06:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is going well so far. The issue here is the facility's security.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi and Ayase are looking into that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're just on standby for a while, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.78,0:06:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what the hell could be on this island, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Gai only knows," it seems.{gai nomi zo shiru lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, Argo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you overheated?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm fired up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.81,0:06:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Shu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He left before us. He said he had a stop to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, Oshima is where his father's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.15,0:07:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I caught this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.59,0:07:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! What a classy lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi, why are you in that ridiculous getup?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your outfit looks splendiferous on you too, {\i1}Madame Ayase{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.07,0:07:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Ouma Kurosu, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a professor at the old Tennozu College.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was also the leading expert on the Apocalypse Virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't {\i1}you{\i0} know about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:08:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't talk about stuff like that at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that he was Haruka's teacher, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Haruka"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.56,0:08:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I don't really remember my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He died ten years ago, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost Christmas, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything changed after that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.53,0:08:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not to visit a grave, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at it with these.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret GHQ facility. What I want is inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rock that started it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we need to get our hands on most right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and the Void you draw will be the key to the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I trust you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tamadate Souta... yeah, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mission begins at 2200.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring him to the designated point by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You make it sound so easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It {\i1}is{\i0} easy. Just use bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bait?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear he's an Egoist fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to use Inori?! That's horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You use something the other person is interested in to bring him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the most basic play there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that "something" is Inori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see there's no point in arguing any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't do it, you don't have to. Just stay in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't gone on a trip with friends in forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming with us, Kanon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? I {\i1}am{\i0} a member of the club, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if in name only.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since Yahiro didn't come...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have anything to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.19,0:10:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.04,0:10:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I were all alone with Yuzuriha, I'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Inori, you've got great skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can I touch you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! It's so smooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about {\i1}here{\i0}, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't... touch there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.88,0:10:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder how Yuzuriha feels about Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.74,0:10:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.98,0:11:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there really nothing between you and Inori?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.15,0:11:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before, there really isn't—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there isn't, I'm going for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going for Inori.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to start tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:11:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mission you drag your friends into...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's certainly not a job that suits Ouma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I disagree. That's what friends are for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.94,0:12:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A life with no adventure in it is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The least a friend can do is stir up a little trouble in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutsugami Gai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.89,0:12:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter. I'm not entirely convinced he's even my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His mother was a no-good woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry this was so sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stars are really pretty, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We hardly ever see them in Tokyo... well, I guess this is Tokyo too, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not a problem. There's no problem with leaving them alone together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so touched by Egoist's music video, I just couldn't contain myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I tried making one of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:48.16,Copy of OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}{\an8\fad(200,200)\blur2}Blooming wildflower{it's that insert song again}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:56.09,Copy of OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}{\an8\fad(200,200)\blur2}I beg you, please tell me{insert song}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's doing something I'd do...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Does he think Inori'll be interested in just any guy who does that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:14:03.97,Copy of OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}{\an8\fad(200,200)\blur2}Why do people fight and hurt each other?{insert song}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Inori!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I don't know you very well yet, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.92,0:14:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When your singing moved me, that feeling was real!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know you better, Inori!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I... really... l-lo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!{t:}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori is my—{nope ntr time}{t:}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.98,0:14:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's the big idea? Don't draw that thing out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.73,0:15:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you been there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no self-control.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Inori is my—!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an unexpected development.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now, Gai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.49,0:15:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be no change of plans. We'll go now, as is. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye-aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Inori is my" {\i1}what{\i0}?{so much jelly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.38,0:15:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all here, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.92,0:15:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi's blinded the guards. The issue is what's inside here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ogumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you confess your feelings, you should do a proper job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.24,0:15:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu, shoot the gate with that camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a Void for opening things?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.08,0:16:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your business?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies, Chief Keido—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.82,0:16:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a wraith passing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could they be on to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this isn't about us. This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.03,0:16:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would a Void like this come from inside Souta?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.94,0:17:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't care less about the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The important thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is that his Void can "open" even a mechanism like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our objective lies ahead. Shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.39,0:17:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:18:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai? What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're withdrawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have known it was you, Keido.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The double grief of a lost bliss is to recall its happy hour in pain"...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.27,0:18:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.12,0:18:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Inori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She went back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:18:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to help you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:19:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have feelings for Inori after all, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you feel that way, then tell me from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never know what you're thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no better!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.03,0:19:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pushy, you have no tact, and you're oblivious to everyone around you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That really bothers me about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.07,0:19:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a hard time dealing with you, Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.98,0:19:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He must hate me now. But that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.95,0:19:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should've been honest from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.45,0:19:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If he was my friend, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Souta?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.98,0:19:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you gave it to me straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you're always kind of distant, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.73,0:20:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, it was a little hard for me to deal with you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.23,0:20:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm glad that you were honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means you've opened up to me, right?{SO DEEP}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.42,0:20:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's a little late to ask this, but... what are Voids?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand them yet, but I get the feeling I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.92,0:20:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, after all, my right hand is touching people's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.08,0:21:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai told me that Voids change along with the states of people's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.47,0:21:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...{t:}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.67,0:21:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So does that mean if I form a bond with someone, my power changes too?{POWER OF FRIENDSHIP}
