Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:13.82,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HA5A85D&}and places a crown of thorns upon your head,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:19.78,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\3c&H98B74E&\blur3}I can take your side, and yours alone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:25.16,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\3c&HA87A51&\blur3}I know your pain and loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:28.29,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an1\blur3}So everything that makes me whole
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.38,0:02:34.80,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)\3c&HD46ACE&}I'll give that to you now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:25.55,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}These days you love me no more
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.17,0:21:32.18,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}nor am I still treasured by you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:40.98,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Now I am all alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.77,0:21:48.86,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}What did you tell me when we parted?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:55.50,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}The words hung in midair and never reached me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.95,0:22:02.25,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}I know my dreams and wishes are illusory
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:08.88,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}and yet I cannot give up on them
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.93,0:22:18.89,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}You said, "Don't let go, hold onto my hand"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.44,0:22:25.90,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}and, "We will always be together"
